<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Damir Aushenov</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhani:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      body {
        background: #000;
        font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      /* â”€â”€ profile header â”€â”€ */
      .profile-header {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a1220 0%, #0d1520 100%);
        border-bottom: 1px solid #1a2a1a;
        padding: 16px 32px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .profile-header img {
        width: 56px;
        height: 56px;
        object-fit: cover;
        object-position: center top;
        border: 2px solid #3a5a3a;
        display: block;
      }

      .profile-header-name {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .profile-header-title {
        margin-top: 4px;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #4db84d;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      /* â”€â”€ nav â”€â”€ */
      nav {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0d1520 0%, #080e18 100%);
        border-bottom: 1px solid #1a2a1a;
      }

      .nav-tabs {
        display: flex;
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0 32px;
      }

      .nav-tabs li a {
        display: block;
        padding: 18px 28px 16px;
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #4db84d;
        border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
        transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
        position: relative;
        top: 1px;
      }

      .nav-tabs li a:hover {
        color: #80e080;
        border-bottom-color: rgba(100, 220, 100, 0.35);
      }

      .nav-tabs li.active a {
        color: #8fff6a;
        border-bottom-color: #8fff6a;
      }

      /* â”€â”€ page body â”€â”€ */
      .page {
        padding: 40px 32px;
      }

      /* â”€â”€ about block â”€â”€ */
      .about-block {
        width: 380px;
        background: rgba(6, 12, 24, 0.82);
        border-top: 2px solid #8fff6a;
        padding: 22px 24px 28px;
      }

      .about-block h2 {
        font-size: 26px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      }

      .about-block p {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: #d0d8e4;
        line-height: 1.65;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      /* â”€â”€ stat grid â”€â”€ */
      .stat-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 18px 12px;
      }

      .stat {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2px;
      }

      .stat-label {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #7a8a9a;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      }

      .stat-value {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
        letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      }

      .stat-value.green { color: #8fff6a; }
      .stat-value.blue  { color: #4ab4ff; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="profile-header">
      <img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="Damir Aushenov" />
      <div>
        <div class="profile-header-name">Damir Aushenov</div>
        <div class="profile-header-title">iOS Developer</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <nav>
      <ul class="nav-tabs">
        <li class="active"><a href="/">Main</a></li>
        <li><a href="/works">My Works</a></li>
        <li><a href="/training">My Training</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="page">
      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
          iOS developer based in Bishkek. I build apps in Swift and SwiftUI,
          and when I'm not coding I'm running roads or lifting in the gym.
          Here I write about development, training, and things I'm building.
        </p>

        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-label">Started Coding</span>
            <span class="stat-value">2016</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-label">Location</span>
            <span class="stat-value">ðŸ‡°ðŸ‡¬ Bishkek</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-label">Experience</span>
            <span class="stat-value">10 yrs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-label">Main Language</span>
            <span class="stat-value blue">Swift</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-label">Specialty</span>
            <span class="stat-value green">iOS / SwiftUI</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
